CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 23, 1952, pg. 15, reads: "Baby Corner ... Cute little Conchita Carmen Garcia celebrated her first birthday Sunday, Feb. 17, with a beautiful cake all for her very own. She is the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Paul Garcia of 1033 Bustrick Heights. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Girls and boys, some wearing party hats, gathered in living room for first birthday party of Conchita Carmen Garcia
